msgid ""
"To minimize the interruption caused by :ref:`election process <replica-"
"set-elections>`, always upgrade the secondaries of the set first, then "
":dbcommand:`step down <replSetStepDown>` the primary, and then upgrade "
"the primary."
msgstr ""

